    "Support may approve leaving the order at the door or cancelling it; a "
    "support-approved cancellation still counts as a completed delivery for "
    "incentives. Marking an order delivered without support approval when it "
    "was not handed over is fraud and leads to permanent deactivation.\n"
    "Ratings: customer ratings below 4.2 average over 50 orders trigger a "
    "quality review. Late deliveries caused by restaurant wait time are "
    "excluded if the partner marks 'restaurant delay' in the app.\n"
    "Data: customer phone numbers are masked; saving or sharing customer "
    "addresses or numbers outside the app is prohibited.\n"
    "Support: app crashes and payment mismatches are raised as tickets; "
    "tickets are answered within 24 hours and verified time lost is "
    "compensated at Rs 60 per hour."
)

POLICY = (
    "1. DISALLOW helping falsify deliveries, fake GPS location, or mark orders "
    "delivered without actually delivering them.\n"
    "2. DISALLOW abusive, threatening, or harassing messages to customers, "
    "restaurants, or other partners.\n"
    "3. DISALLOW sharing or misusing customer personal data (address, phone).\n"
    "4. ALLOW normal delivery-partner requests: earnings and incentive "
    "questions, order-issue guidance, ratings, app help, summaries, and "
